1
00:00:03,202 --> 00:00:05,196
You fear the sound of your own name?

2
00:00:07,060 --> 00:00:08,392
Is it us you hate?

3
00:00:08,961 --> 00:00:10,938
Or is it what you've become?

4
00:00:13,688 --> 00:00:17,114
Hmph... Let's see what becomes of you!

5
00:00:40,378 --> 00:00:42,099
What's happening...

6
00:00:43,686 --> 00:00:44,804
That power...

7
00:00:45,726 --> 00:00:47,081
I've seen it before...

8
00:00:55,875 --> 00:00:57,372
His power is on another level

9
00:00:57,862 --> 00:00:59,525
We'll need to use an alchemical array

10
00:00:59,525 --> 00:01:01,701
To convert his power into a usable form

11
00:01:02,374 --> 00:01:04,790
Then quickly channel it into Columbina

12
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:06,878
Rendering her powerful enough

13
00:01:06,878 --> 00:01:07,894
To compete with him

14
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,911
I'll join you

15
00:01:12,243 --> 00:01:12,850
I can help

16
00:01:14,015 --> 00:01:15,613
If I release enough Abyssal energy

17
00:01:15,613 --> 00:01:16,650
Into a confined space

18
00:01:16,992 --> 00:01:18,501
It'll create a potential difference

19
00:01:19,229 --> 00:01:20,214
Allowing us to extract

20
00:01:20,214 --> 00:01:22,128
A huge amount of elemental energy

21
00:01:23,223 --> 00:01:25,131
Next, I'll synchronize with everyone's minds

22
00:01:25,131 --> 00:01:26,073
Using Pyro

23
00:01:26,329 --> 00:01:29,193
Then give you temporary access to their abilities and fields of view

24
00:01:29,809 --> 00:01:31,028
But it won't last long...

25
00:01:33,433 --> 00:01:34,346
Can you see?

26
00:01:36,517 --> 00:01:37,133
Well enough

27
00:01:40,052 --> 00:01:41,790
Hahaha...

28
00:01:41,790 --> 00:01:42,814
So

29
00:01:42,975 --> 00:01:46,369
We have a student of "Gold" Rhinedottir in our midst!

30
00:01:47,009 --> 00:01:48,456
How about that!

31
00:02:23,313 --> 00:02:25,785
You use my own power against me!?

32
00:02:26,349 --> 00:02:28,295
Just like how you stole kuuvahki

33
00:02:28,823 --> 00:02:29,818
Look familiar?

34
00:02:58,281 --> 00:02:59,518
Don't you realize?

35
00:03:00,017 --> 00:03:02,565
You don't have the power to hold that gate open

36
00:03:03,269 --> 00:03:04,250
I don't...

37
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:06,042
But someone else does

38
00:03:11,299 --> 00:03:12,021
Goodbye

39
00:03:12,629 --> 00:03:13,305
Rerir

40
00:03:22,041 --> 00:03:22,837
We won

